, \"to\": 3283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before the Rio Olympics in 2016, the polluted Guanabara Bay made headlines.\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3296, \"end\": 3308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.055469123672346e-23, \"text\": \"Rio Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the polluted Guanabara Bay\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3344}, {\"ngram\": \"headlines\", \"from\": 3350, \"to\": 3359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Italian double world champion Gregorio Paltrinieri told Italian media in January.\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3362, \"end\": 3369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9737023762348501, \"rank\": 0.026956780728211234, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 3392, \"end\": 3412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregorio_Paltrinieri\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gregorio Paltrinieri\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregorio_Paltrinieri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregorio_Paltrinieri\"}, {\"begin\": 3418, \"end\": 3425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9737023762348501, \"rank\": 0.026956780728211234, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even if the water is dirty, I would rather swim in an electric atmosphere in the centre of Paris than in an anonymous stretch of water.\\\"\", 